(41, 14, 16, 42, 22, 35, 35, 'made ready the passover', 'Provision and Preparation', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparation and provision. In Mark, the disciples prepare for the Passover as instructed, while in Luke, Jesus reminds them of their previous lack of need when sent without provisions.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
